msgctxt "108_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"I consulted a lawyer. He got me off the hook with those\r\n"
"loan sharks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"From now on, I'm your customer. Thank you so much for taking\r\n"
"me on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Happy to help. Of course, you still have a mountain of debt.\r\n"
"You'll have to work it off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Yes, of course!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"Um... Would you please accept this? I know it may seem odd\r\n"
"coming from a borrower, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, sure. Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "I have to get to work. See you around!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228_Akiyama"
msgid "(He'll be okay... I think.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Okay! It's now or never! Hopefully they won't kill me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"...No! I'm going to live! I'm going to get out of this\r\n"
"and get my life together! Here I go! Aaaaahhhhh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312_Akiyama"
msgid "(Well... I'm eager to see how this plays out.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "384_Akiyama"
msgid "(It's been a while. I suppose I should check in on him.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "408_Akiyama"
msgid "Uh, hey, pal. What are you doing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "420_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Don't try to stop me! I have to kill myself!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "432_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Oh. Well, you're probably not going to die if you jump from\r\n"
"there. Not unless you can't swim."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "444_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Huh? Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "456_Onlooker"
msgid "You idiot, stay out of this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "468_Onlooker"
msgid "It was just startin' to get good, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "480_Onlooker"
msgid "Well, that sucked. Let's go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "504_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh? I'm the bad guy here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "576_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "...Sorry to drag you into this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "588_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"No kidding. I feel like a real ass trying to play the good\r\n"
"guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "600_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "I'm sorry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "612_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"So, why kill yourself? I'm already involved－I may as well\r\n"
"hear you out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "624_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"I was a little short on money, so I went to a loan shark.\r\n"
"And long story short, I now owe more than I can ever hope to\r\n"
"repay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "636_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"You should have consulted a lawyer right away. They would\r\n"
"have shut down any threats in no time flat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "648_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"Well, the loan sharks seem to know that. They said they'd\r\n"
"kill me if I went to a lawyer. Plus, they're watching my\r\n"
"every move, so I couldn't call one even if I wanted to..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "660_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"So you settled on killing yourself? Didn't really think that\r\n"
"through, did you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "672_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"It's always this way with me. I fail at everything I do.\r\n"
"This debt isn't even mine－I was forced into being a\r\n"
"guarantor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "684_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"And now, it turns out I can't even kill myself properly. I\r\n"
"don't know what to do anymore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "696_Akiyama"
msgid "Hm. Depressing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "708_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"But you're in luck for a change. After all, it was none\r\n"
"other than me who stopped you from jumping."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "720_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"I haven't introduced myself. I'm Akiyama. I run a\r\n"
"moneylending business by the name of Sky Finance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "732_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"What? You're a loan shark, too!? Oh, I get it. You seem all\r\n"
"friendly at first, then watch, you're going to bleed me dry\r\n"
"just like the rest of them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "744_Akiyama"
msgid "Now, now. Just hear me out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "756_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"The loan sharks and I are a little different when it comes\r\n"
"to loan applications. I have only one condition－that you\r\n"
"pass the test I assign."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "768_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Test?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "780_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Right. If you pass, you qualify for a loan with no maximum\r\n"
"limit, no interest, and no collateral. That's our specialty."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "792_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"No limit? No interest, no collateral? How is that even\r\n"
"possible?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "804_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Let me worry about that. So, what do you say? Care to take\r\n"
"my test?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "816_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Er－ Yes! Yes, please!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "828_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay then, let's get to work. Your test is simple."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "840_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Go to the lender's office right now, and tell them you're\r\n"
"going to a lawyer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "852_Desperate Debtor"
msgid ""
"But, I can't! I told you, if I so much as think about\r\n"
"talking to a lawyer, they'll kill me! Why would you make me\r\n"
"do that!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "864_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"You can whine all you want, but that's my test. It's up to\r\n"
"you. You in or out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "876_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Urk... But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "888_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Look, you weren't doing a very good job, but you were\r\n"
"trying to kill yourself, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "900_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Try using that nothing-left-to-lose attitude to face your\r\n"
"problem head-on, not run away from it. This could be your\r\n"
"last chance, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "912_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Akiyama-san, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "924_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Okay, I get it. I'll do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "936_Akiyama"
msgid "Great, let's not waste any time. Where's their office?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "948_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "They're over in West Shofukucho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "960_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Good. Off you go, then. Don't worry, I'm with you all the\r\n"
"way. If they kill you, I'll spring for your funeral."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "972_Desperate Debtor"
msgid "Thank you.... Okay. Here I go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "996_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"(Will he actually go through with this? He said the lender's\r\n"
"in West Shofukucho. I'd better go take a look.)"
msgstr ""